author: Yuu
text:
I know not many will care about what I will write now but still I want to get it out:

Im thankful to the entire Hololive Fanbase and Community, for being a comfy and welcoming Community. No matter which VTuber it is, May it be Rushia, Calli, Ina, Gura, Watame, Towa, Okayu, Sora, Korone and many many more. You all rock, because you make someones life. Even if you dont Pay and just lurk, Or being a Giga Chad paying hundreds and thousands for VTubers and writing much. YOU make the day of a Person. YOU make happiness and comfyness with how you are. The VTubers may got many problems but they will always remember. Remember what? Remember that you, that single one person, Is watching her. And from one comes many, as we are a big Community, We are WORLDWIDE! 

Many of them had problems, but they take a Smile and go on with their lifes because they know "Tomorrow/in some days I stream again and see the People that are watching and enjoying my content, my personality and how I am".

Many of you are facing difficult situations, Im certainly Sure. I myself included. But as a Community, we stand together for what we are!

Dont forget what you are, Enjoy every Moment that lasts, you may never know what comes the next day!

Best wishes and good Streams!
Sincerely
- German Hololive Fan "Yuu"
